         BDSM porn set in 18th century England - in the days of de Sade and the
         Hellfire Clubs, in other words. Chains, whips, and the occasional branding
         iron. The artwork starts out as sepia in the first book, and then kind of
         verges towards full-colour later on but never quite gets there, which gives
         it a rather distinctive look.

         There was a fourth volume published in the original French after the
         artbook, but I'm not sure if that one has ever been professionally
         translated.
